{"tid":554363,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[虧佬救星] 一人一個痴撚線既保暖方法","createTime":"2018-02-08T12:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T03:36:22.000Z","uid":29150,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2b4cf3b210d749179f9bc246633230533d570f","tid":554363,"uid":29150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n1. 戴手套 ( 要露指玩手機）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/201616_817864071164870598e14b2a74b5b31b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F201616_817864071164870598e14b2a74b5b31b.png&h=dd871a23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 暖包x2<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/201500_6c92740404e47736b9b875913b74a963.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F201500_6c92740404e47736b9b875913b74a963.png&h=f1f09c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/201532_f8c707cec3e1ad566c194f9d113364da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F201532_f8c707cec3e1ad566c194f9d113364da.png&h=9453c043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 放一個或以上入手套， 跟住就係等。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/201739_2eaa34bc8e9e6800df325015dcb073d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F201739_2eaa34bc8e9e6800df325015dcb073d0.png&h=e8698d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 等10分鍾。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/202023_a757109076659bc9756931604e4d84b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F202023_a757109076659bc9756931604e4d84b3.png&h=c2cd302d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸： 病都痴撚左線&amp; 病左都要番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43beacd7f9a3c2247c210d48e7bbeae32e500406","tid":554363,"uid":29150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:27:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb927e786c9f08ac448bef0823e57dfe1cb859ff","tid":554363,"uid":15406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"有啲手套唔洗露指都用到電話"},{"pid":"5eeaa93c90d0ef18be3f48804832a1e670c5f284","tid":554363,"uid":62471,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:32:25.000Z","msg":"揸住碌鳩"},{"pid":"403d02bb56b45f879be0f113498ebd9760b6b030","tid":554363,"uid":29150,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb927e786c9f08ac448bef0823e57dfe1cb859ff","tid":554363,"uid":15406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"有啲手套唔洗露指都用到電話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"傳熱手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ?"},{"pid":"a0ab0b3f07be501ee9a942b53aa29fc6c14efe14","tid":554363,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"403d02bb56b45f879be0f113498ebd9760b6b030","tid":554363,"uid":29150,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb927e786c9f08ac448bef0823e57dfe1cb859ff","tid":554363,"uid":15406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"有啲手套唔洗露指都用到電話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"傳熱手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e46c617bec1149f597a3ab5173c7a8f3cfced5b","tid":554363,"uid":80015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:44:26.000Z","msg":"氣溫回升啦喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1adfe8afe8e209b844f3e0fa87684aea23261cf","tid":554363,"uid":30028,"like":0,"d